        {
          "type": "heading",
          "value": "Nano Editor Overview"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Nano is the easiest text editor for beginners. It displays helpful shortcuts at the bottom of the screen and does not require special modes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slideId": 3,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "value": "Working Inside nano"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Once nano is open, you can start typing immediately. There are no special modes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slideId": 4,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "value": "Common nano Shortcuts"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "Ctrl + O – Save the file",
            "Ctrl + X – Exit nano",
            "Ctrl + W – Search text",
            "Ctrl + K – Cut a line",
            "Ctrl + U – Paste a line"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
